---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Custom Tape Measure Supplier | OEM Tape Measures by WOOKTOOL"
  description="WOOKTOOL offers custom tape measure services including logo, shell color, tape length, material, packaging, hang card, and private-label branding."
  path="/custom-tape-measure/"
>
  <section class="page-intro"><div><p class="eyebrow">Custom tape measure</p><h1>Custom Tape Measure Supplier</h1><p>Create private-label tape measures with custom logo, shell color, tape length, blade finish, packaging, hang card, and barcode requirements.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner grid two">
      <div>
        <h2>Customization options</h2>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Logo printing on shell or label area</li>
          <li>Shell color selection for brand programs</li>
          <li>Tape length and blade material choices</li>
          <li>Hook, clip, and wrist strap options</li>
          <li>Blister card, color box, display box, and hang card packaging</li>
          <li>Private-label barcode and carton mark support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <img class="product-square-image" src="/images/products/custom-tape-measure-1000.png" alt="WOOKTOOL custom tape measure supplier product image" width="1000" height="1000" />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section soft">
    <div class="section-inner grid three">
      <article class="process-card"><h3>1. Confirm requirements</h3><p>Share product type, logo, tape length, packaging, quantity, and target market.</p></article>
      <article class="process-card"><h3>2. Sample and quotation</h3><p>Review cost, sample options, production timeline, and packaging artwork needs.</p></article>
      <article class="process-card"><h3>3. Production and QC</h3><p>After approval, production follows confirmed specifications with inspection before shipment.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Private-label details</p>
          <h2>Common details to confirm before production</h2>
        </div>
        <p>These details make quotation, sampling, artwork review, and final production much smoother for importer and distributor orders.</p>
      </div>
      <table class="spec-table">
        <tbody>
          <tr><th>Branding</th><td>Logo file, print position, shell color, tape blade marking, packaging artwork</td></tr>
          <tr><th>Product</th><td>Length, width, blade coating, lock style, hook style, belt clip, wrist strap</td></tr>
          <tr><th>Packaging</th><td>Blister card, hang card, color box, display box, barcode label, carton mark</td></tr>
          <tr><th>Order planning</th><td>Target quantity, sample deadline, delivery date, destination market, inspection requirements</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTA title="Build a custom tape measure for your brand" primaryLabel="Get Custom Solution" />
</BaseLayout>
